name: GM
description:
GM

This is the beginning of an illustration series to amazing thread, started by 6529 on twitter that serves as NFT slang explanation for newcomers, as well as a collective item for those who know the way

quote from @punk6529 aka 6529: "gm means "good morning"  

We say good morning to each other because we are a friendly happy optimistic global community and it is nice to say good morning to your friends as you start your day"
